<h4>Page Borders Options</h4>

<ol>

<li>Make sure the <strong>Page Border Tab</strong> is selected.</li>
<li>Choose the Style, Color, and Width of the border for the page. Notice that when you click on Art, you have choices of pictures to apply <strong>Border Art</strong>.</li>
<li>Choose whether to apply the border to the <strong>Whole Document</strong> or to the a selected section.</li>
<li>Click Ok.</li>
</ol>

